WEBVTT

00:10.265 --> 00:11.600
Do not panic.

00:12.309 --> 00:13.560
Remain in formation.

00:14.561 --> 00:16.145
Keep your mounts as long as you can.

00:16.688 --> 00:18.106
These men mean to see you dead.

00:19.191 --> 00:20.526
They will fight savagely.

00:20.609 --> 00:22.277
As will we, my lord.

00:30.160 --> 00:32.371
Green fucking boys!

00:33.956 --> 00:35.541
What of the Kingsguard?

00:35.624 --> 00:38.210
Take heart, Beesbury.
I will handle the Kingsguard.

00:39.211 --> 00:41.672
Their oath forbids them
to harm a prince of the blood.

00:41.755 --> 00:44.132
Is that honorable, Your Grace?

00:44.800 --> 00:46.260
The gods will let us know.

00:46.343 --> 00:48.011
Mother loved you best, huh?

00:50.138 --> 00:51.348
Shame.

00:52.057 --> 00:54.768
No man fights so fierce
as one neglected by his mother.

01:00.482 --> 01:01.483
Be vigilant.

01:02.317 --> 01:03.443
Don't die.

01:10.742 --> 01:11.868
Ser.

01:11.952 --> 01:13.161
My lance, squire.

01:29.303 --> 01:31.096
You best be here when I get back.

01:34.600 --> 01:37.561
Rob me, and I'll hunt you down

01:37.644 --> 01:38.603
with dogs.

01:40.814 --> 01:42.065
Woof!

02:02.169 --> 02:05.797
May the Seven bear witness
to our solemn and bloody offering.

02:07.883 --> 02:11.136
May they peer inside our mortal hearts
and find the truth.

02:13.055 --> 02:15.265
May the Warrior grant victory
to the innocent...

02:16.475 --> 02:18.769
and reveal the guilty in their falseness.

02:20.771 --> 02:24.691
May death sustain life.

03:08.402 --> 03:10.654
Up! Up! Go!

03:12.989 --> 03:15.575
Up! Up! Go!

03:16.576 --> 03:17.744
Hyah!

04:20.599 --> 04:22.225
Fuck!

04:35.197 --> 04:37.282
Ma... ma...

04:41.661 --> 04:42.996
Ma...

04:45.791 --> 04:47.250
I'm sorry.

05:00.680 --> 05:01.723
-Don't!
-Ah!

05:01.807 --> 05:03.350
What the fuck are you doing?

05:04.184 --> 05:05.519
He's got a seal.

05:05.602 --> 05:06.728
He's dying.

05:07.979 --> 05:09.898
If we can get him off the hill,
might someone pay us

05:09.981 --> 05:12.025
for his ransom. Quick!

05:44.140 --> 05:45.308
Fuck!

05:51.648 --> 05:52.983
Do you know any words?

05:54.776 --> 05:55.986
What's that mean?

05:57.112 --> 06:00.699
You see, when these bloody highborn spoil,
you gotta say words for them.

06:01.825 --> 06:02.826
Oh.

06:03.910 --> 06:05.954
-Why?
-So they don't end up

06:06.037 --> 06:07.706
in no hell with the rest of us.

06:11.918 --> 06:13.503
I don't know any words.

06:17.591 --> 06:19.968
Right. Check his mouth.

06:20.969 --> 06:23.013
I know a witch who pays copper for teeth.

06:23.096 --> 06:24.806
I am your queen!

06:24.890 --> 06:26.558
Wipe my arse, liege.

06:28.018 --> 06:29.769
What?

06:29.853 --> 06:31.354
You never seen a man die before?

06:32.522 --> 06:33.899
Yeah.

06:33.982 --> 06:35.984
But not like that.

06:37.569 --> 06:39.070
He was crying for his mother.

06:39.154 --> 06:40.447
Yeah, what's she gonna do?

06:41.197 --> 06:43.533
Lift the fucking horse off his legs?

06:43.617 --> 06:44.910
Shit, come on.

07:05.138 --> 07:06.306
Right, come on.

07:06.389 --> 07:07.599
Come on.

07:09.976 --> 07:13.605
I just don't know why we're in
such a rush to leave anymore.

07:13.688 --> 07:17.359
The war is over.
The Black Dragon is dead.

07:18.735 --> 07:20.654
Ferret said we're all
to get free bread now.

07:20.737 --> 07:21.738
Are you stupid?

07:23.323 --> 07:24.449
Nothing's over.

07:27.285 --> 07:29.704
Don't you remember when Pudding killed
Cedric's little brother?

07:29.788 --> 07:31.498
-That was an accident.
-Aye.

07:31.581 --> 07:33.416
And we all figured
that'd be the end to it,

07:33.500 --> 07:35.335
only for Cedric to come back a year later

07:35.418 --> 07:37.962
and near burn down half of Flea Bottom
trying to kill Pudding.

07:41.299 --> 07:42.884
No one forgets shit.

07:42.968 --> 07:45.470
You hurt someone, they hurt you back.

07:47.013 --> 07:48.807
If you want to stay, fine.

07:48.890 --> 07:51.184
But Flea Bottom
is full up on people hurting.

07:51.935 --> 07:53.269
It's tinder waiting to catch.

08:07.200 --> 08:08.159
Stay calm now.

08:09.703 --> 08:10.704
You'll be alright.

08:25.218 --> 08:26.261
Rafe.

08:30.140 --> 08:31.141
Dunk.

08:38.648 --> 08:39.899
What's in the bag?

08:42.610 --> 08:43.611
Rats.

08:45.280 --> 08:46.281
Oh!

08:47.741 --> 08:48.783
Rats!

08:50.744 --> 08:51.828
Let's see 'em, then.

09:07.385 --> 09:08.595
Fucking cunt!

09:11.264 --> 09:12.724
You shouldn't have done that.

09:12.807 --> 09:14.059
You know what Alester's like.

09:14.142 --> 09:17.729
Aye, and the evil bastard was about to
steal our shit, so I stole his.

09:17.812 --> 09:19.022
That's not what I meant.

09:19.105 --> 09:20.607
Oh, is that not what you meant?

09:20.690 --> 09:22.192
I'm doing him a favor.

09:22.275 --> 09:24.611
This ale tastes as sour
as the queen's own brew.

09:25.612 --> 09:26.613
Come on.

09:31.701 --> 09:34.621
We'll all be plundering
that tomb for a dragon's age.

09:37.916 --> 09:38.917
Hey!

09:39.709 --> 09:41.586
Daemon's rebellion is over.

09:41.669 --> 09:43.588
Take your Blackfyre leather elsewhere.

09:53.973 --> 09:55.433
Is it enough?

09:56.184 --> 09:57.852
It's enough.

10:08.696 --> 10:10.782
Hey, don't lose your nerve now.

10:12.033 --> 10:13.284
The shit part's done.

10:14.410 --> 10:15.995
I know.

10:16.079 --> 10:18.123
We'll be sailing off
into all kinds of adventures.

10:18.206 --> 10:20.708
-Don't you want that?
-I do.

10:20.792 --> 10:21.918
I just...

10:24.170 --> 10:25.171
What?

10:27.715 --> 10:29.926
What if the Free Cities
are no better than here?

10:31.636 --> 10:32.804
What if they're worse?

10:33.680 --> 10:36.516
Then we'll go someplace else.

10:36.599 --> 10:38.434
What if it's all shit?

10:38.518 --> 10:42.272
Every place?
What if this is the best there is?

10:44.107 --> 10:45.692
That would be quite sad.

10:50.530 --> 10:54.617
And what if my mother
comes back for me?

10:57.996 --> 11:00.665
I'm not stupid. I know she's dead.

11:01.666 --> 11:05.295
But what if she's just trying to get away
from wherever she is?

11:05.879 --> 11:06.880
Like we are?

11:06.963 --> 11:09.674
If I leave, then how will she find me?

11:10.800 --> 11:13.052
You are fucking stupid sometimes.

11:14.179 --> 11:16.222
If your mother was alive,

11:16.306 --> 11:17.682
she's not coming back for you.

11:17.765 --> 11:19.100
You don't know that.

11:19.184 --> 11:22.312
I know I never got nothin'
by waiting around.

11:22.395 --> 11:23.938
You want a family?

11:25.481 --> 11:28.109
Go out there, get a family.

11:29.861 --> 11:31.613
I just want to be with you.

11:32.822 --> 11:34.365
'Cause you love me.

11:35.575 --> 11:36.576
Yeah.

11:40.455 --> 11:41.456
Well...

11:43.082 --> 11:44.709
I love you too, don't I?

11:47.754 --> 11:49.130
And I'm going.

11:50.715 --> 11:52.759
So, you best be coming with me.

12:00.433 --> 12:03.895
This city is too small for us, Dunk.

12:06.314 --> 12:07.899
Let's show her our arse.

12:32.966 --> 12:34.092
Right, come on, Dunk.

12:45.395 --> 12:46.980
Dunk, get a move on.

13:03.913 --> 13:05.581
Two fares to the Free Cities.

13:09.210 --> 13:11.421
What? Our silver don't spend?

13:11.504 --> 13:13.047
Price is double.

13:13.131 --> 13:15.717
You're not the only ones
who mean to get the fuck out of here.

13:17.176 --> 13:19.262
-Right. Move!
-Wait, get off me!

13:19.345 --> 13:20.430
Rafe.

13:21.639 --> 13:22.807
Fuck!

13:24.058 --> 13:25.935
-I suppose you're happy.
-What?

13:26.019 --> 13:28.646
You've got plenty of time to wait around
for your dead mother now.

13:33.735 --> 13:34.986
I'm sorry.

13:36.362 --> 13:38.031
We'll find a way.

13:44.954 --> 13:46.706
You got quick hands, girl.

13:50.835 --> 13:52.628
I used to have quick hands.

14:08.686 --> 14:10.855
I'll have me ale-skin back.

14:13.775 --> 14:15.693
I sold it.

14:19.822 --> 14:21.366
No! No, no.

14:21.449 --> 14:22.784
We can get it back.

14:29.207 --> 14:30.917
Oh, what's that?

14:33.252 --> 14:34.962
Fuck off! Give it back.

14:35.963 --> 14:37.006
Give it back.

14:44.097 --> 14:45.348
Holding out on us.

14:45.431 --> 14:46.557
That's ours.

14:47.642 --> 14:50.103
Little gutter rats don't have silver.

14:50.186 --> 14:51.270
Only little thieves.

14:51.354 --> 14:53.856
We didn't thieve nothing.
We earned that.

14:53.940 --> 14:56.359
Stealing from dead nobles
is still stealing.

14:56.442 --> 14:58.236
And what's stealing from us?

14:59.320 --> 15:01.447
-That's life.
-Yeah.

15:07.870 --> 15:08.913
Huh.

15:08.996 --> 15:10.498
Come on.

15:10.581 --> 15:12.291
Rafe, let's go.

15:14.085 --> 15:15.086
Rafe!

15:18.131 --> 15:19.132
Go on.

15:22.718 --> 15:23.761
Rafe.

15:41.028 --> 15:42.780
You little cunt.

15:47.952 --> 15:49.120
No!

16:10.266 --> 16:11.809
Ah! Fuck!

16:16.606 --> 16:17.857
Stick him.

16:20.610 --> 16:22.403
In the name of the Mother!

16:23.654 --> 16:25.364
Leave that boy be!

17:39.230 --> 17:40.731
Get out of my way!

17:50.366 --> 17:51.617
I'm sorry.

18:38.497 --> 18:41.751
Maybe I'll have some of those apples.

18:41.834 --> 18:43.210
Yes...

18:43.294 --> 18:46.339
-Oh, you old fool.
-Sorry. I'm sorry.

19:08.486 --> 19:12.114
Hey, boys. Did you miss me? Yeah.

22:24.640 --> 22:26.809
Ah, you old fool!

23:08.475 --> 23:09.602
Get up.

24:57.668 --> 24:59.044
Come on!

26:19.875 --> 26:21.293
Aerion!

26:31.512 --> 26:33.889
My boy! My boy!

26:51.532 --> 26:52.741
Get up.

26:53.992 --> 26:54.993
Get up, ser!

26:57.621 --> 26:59.206
Get up, Dunk!

27:00.457 --> 27:01.458
Yield.

27:02.459 --> 27:03.961
Yield!

27:08.340 --> 27:09.842
Yield!

27:46.461 --> 27:49.423
Get up. Get up, ser.

28:04.605 --> 28:05.898
He's dead!

28:08.192 --> 28:09.484
It's over!

28:14.448 --> 28:15.866
Get up, ser!

28:17.326 --> 28:18.410
Get up!

28:20.412 --> 28:21.413
Get up!

28:22.414 --> 28:23.790
Get up, Ser Duncan!

28:25.250 --> 28:27.836
Get up, ser. Get up!

28:31.840 --> 28:33.717
Get up.

28:35.761 --> 28:38.555
Wait!

29:09.086 --> 29:11.380
Up! Up! Up! Up!

30:26.038 --> 30:28.457
I yield. I yield.

31:11.375 --> 31:13.251
Tell him!

31:13.335 --> 31:15.837
Tell him! Tell him!

31:17.631 --> 31:18.882
Tell him!

31:22.594 --> 31:23.637
I...

31:25.263 --> 31:27.432
I withdraw my accusation.

31:49.121 --> 31:50.330
That's it.

31:51.289 --> 31:52.416
Come on.

31:53.959 --> 31:54.960
Steady now.

31:55.669 --> 31:56.878
I'll have to cut that mail off you.

31:58.630 --> 31:59.464
The others.

31:59.548 --> 32:01.842
Has anyone died?

32:01.925 --> 32:04.177
Beesbury and Hardyng, in the first charge.

32:05.303 --> 32:06.304
Gods be good.

32:06.388 --> 32:09.766
The lance point drove the rings
deep into his flesh.

32:09.850 --> 32:11.685
One moment, I felt drunk.

32:12.477 --> 32:14.438
The next, like I'm dying.

32:16.189 --> 32:19.359
We'll get drunk,
then we'll pour boiling oil on it.

32:19.443 --> 32:20.819
That's how the maesters do it.

32:20.902 --> 32:22.028
Wine. Not oil.

32:23.029 --> 32:24.823
Oil will kill him.

32:24.906 --> 32:27.701
I'll send Maester Yormwell
to have a look at him

32:27.784 --> 32:29.494
when he's done tending to my brother.

32:32.247 --> 32:33.915
Your Grace.

32:35.208 --> 32:36.710
I am your man.

32:38.211 --> 32:40.547
Please. Your man.

32:42.841 --> 32:44.718
I need good men, Ser Duncan.

32:46.928 --> 32:48.180
The realm.

32:55.687 --> 32:58.940
Ser Raymun, my helm,
if you would be so kind.

32:59.024 --> 33:00.358
-At once, Your Grace.
-Alright.

33:00.442 --> 33:01.818
You're alright. You're alright.

33:01.902 --> 33:05.280
Visor's... visor's cracked.

33:06.865 --> 33:08.200
My fingers feel...

33:10.327 --> 33:12.037
fingers feel like wood.

33:14.956 --> 33:16.291
Goodman Pate.

33:16.374 --> 33:17.459
A hand.

33:20.837 --> 33:22.839
The helm, it's crushed
down the back, Your Grace.

33:22.923 --> 33:24.174
It's smashed into the gorget.

33:24.257 --> 33:25.884
My brother's mace, most like.

33:27.219 --> 33:28.970
He's strong.

33:36.853 --> 33:37.854
Gods be good.

33:51.535 --> 33:53.036
No.

33:55.872 --> 33:57.374
No, no! No.

33:57.457 --> 33:59.584
No, no, Your Grace. Your Grace.

34:00.210 --> 34:02.128
Your Grace, get up, ser.

34:02.212 --> 34:04.548
Get up, ser! No!

34:05.465 --> 34:06.341
No!

34:07.384 --> 34:08.385
Please!

34:12.305 --> 34:15.183
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

34:20.438 --> 34:21.523
Get up!

34:23.233 --> 34:24.233
I'm sorry.
